            <title><![CDATA[Ikea is the latest major retailer to bet on &#8216;buy now, pay later&#8217;]]></title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;Ikea wants to make it easier to buy inexpensive items on credit by jumping on the &amp;#x2018;buy now, pay later&amp;#x2019; bandwagon. Is this actually good for consumers? &lt;/p&gt;
