            <title><![CDATA[Olivia Rodrigo&#8217;s &#8216;brutal&#8217; shows the power and potential of Apple]]></title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;It&amp;#x2019;s a video for a hit song by one of the planet&amp;#x2019;s top pop stars, and it also happens to be an ad for iPad, Apple Music, and more.&lt;/p&gt;
