            <title><![CDATA[&#8216;Yes, we&#8217;re ugly, but we&#8217;re one-of-a-kind&#8217;: How Crocs went from laughingstock to red carpet]]></title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;Crocs&amp;#x2019;s magic formula has been to capitalize on the intense hatred of the brand. But how long can this continue? &lt;/p&gt;
