            <title><![CDATA[The centerpiece of Microsoft&#8217;s massive new expansion is 550 feet underground]]></title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;The crowning jewel of the tech giant&amp;#x2019;s new campus expansion isn&amp;#x2019;t a flying saucer or a glass mountain. It&amp;#x2019;s a geothermal energy plant&amp;#x2014;and one of the largest in North America. &lt;/p&gt;
